data.description: Spacious 4 bedroom, 3 bathroom home close to Bruins High School and Sawtooth Elementry! This property has something for everyone! Large dining, two masters bedrooms, living room & family room or formal dining on the main level as well as a large downstairs with family/flex room, could make a great man cave or extra living room for the kids. There's an additional room in the basement for extra storage, a 5th bedroom, or turn it into a walkin closet and convert the space into an extra large primary bedroom! The laundry room has space for a half bath! Large back yard has above ground pool with a deck. Also included is an above ground play house with a tree house feeling, equpied with climbing wall and slide!. The NEW furnace comes with a warranty!  This home is being sold as is!
